This is Pomorsky Unicode 1.0, a decorative font for Church Slavonic typography.

COPYRIGHT INFORMATION

The Pomorsky typeface was originally designed by Nikita Simmons. Edited and reencoded for Unicode by Aleksandr Andreev.

